headline: GTA Online
subtitle: 2X GTA$ and RP on VIP Work and Challenges
content:
Executives aren’t all empty suits, you know. Some like to roll the sleeves up on their overpriced sport coat and get their hands caked in filth. If that sounds like you, you’ll be pleased to hear that completing any VIP Work and Challenges this week will pay out doubly — both in GTA$ and RP.

Want to get involved in some white-collar crime? Open up the Interaction Menu, navigate to the SecuroServ section, and select any of the available VIP/CEO Work missions.
